name: Luccy
description: Luccy is a community-driven meme coin built on the Binance Smart Chain (BSC). With a strong emphasis on fostering a solid and vibrant community, Luccy aims to become a leading player in the meme coin ecosystem, surpassing the popularity of existing dog and frog coins. Through innovative features, a dedicated team, and an engaged community, Luccy seeks to establish itself as a prominent and enduring presence in the cryptocurrency space.
